                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="menarinimaster/components/text"
                            text="&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot;>&#xa;    &lt;tbody>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td>&lt;img src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/MENARINI-GROUP-Logo-2017_300.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Menarini Group Logo&quot; longdesc=&quot;Menarini Group Logo&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/Logo-Comune-Firenze-giglio.jpg&quot; />&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;    &lt;/tbody>&#xa;&lt;/table>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;&quot;>Lucia Aleotti:&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;&quot;>&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo; We are proud to have given tangible support to tens of Florentine families in need&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>Florence, 26th October 2017 &amp;ndash; The idea was to help cope with the housing crisis. The aim was to provide a safe and comfortable home to families in economic difficulty. Four years have gone by since &lt;strong>Menarini&lt;/strong> launched their commitment to renovating the first public housing units owned by the &lt;strong>Florence Town Council&lt;/strong>. Since then, the inauguration of new and renovated apartments has become a regular appointment.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>This year Menarini has continued to respect its commitment by funding the complete renovation of &amp;nbsp;10 housing units in residential areas in the Municipality of Florence, bringing the total number of apartments renovated to 40.&amp;nbsp; This time the housing units are situated in&amp;nbsp; &lt;strong>Florence&amp;rsquo;s 2&lt;sup>nd&lt;/sup> and 3&lt;sup>rd&lt;/sup> Districts&lt;/strong>&amp;nbsp; and vary in size from 50 to 70 square metres.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>Menarini funded the restructuring of the housing units making them safe and secure with a restoration of the electrical, mechanical and heating systems, replacement of kitchen and bathroom fittings as well as a checking of the fixtures. The renovation, which took several months to complete, has now made these homes comfortable, welcoming and, above all, safe.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>The ceremony for the handing over of the keys to the apartments took place today, in the 3&lt;sup>rd&lt;/sup> district in the Sorgane area of the city, in the presence of &lt;strong>the Mayor of the City of Florence,&lt;/strong> &lt;strong>Dario Nardella,&amp;nbsp; the Town Counsellor &amp;nbsp;for Housing, Sara Funaro&lt;/strong>, the &lt;strong>Chairman of Casa Spa, Luca Talluri&lt;/strong>, as well as the Chairman and Vice Chairman of&lt;strong> the Menarini Pharmaceutical Group, Lucia and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti.&lt;/strong>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&lt;strong>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/consegna_case.jpg&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot; />&lt;/strong>&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;em style=&quot;letter-spacing: normal;&quot;>From the&amp;nbsp;left: Mayor of&amp;nbsp;Florence, &lt;strong>Dario Nardella&lt;/strong> with &lt;strong>Lucia Aleotti&lt;/strong>, Chairman of Menarini, &lt;strong>Sara Funaro&lt;/strong>, Town Counsellor for Housing,&amp;nbsp;and &lt;strong>Luca Talluri&lt;/strong>, Chairman of Casa Spa&lt;/em>&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;ldquo;The city of Florence thanks the Menarini Pharmaceutical Group and the Aleotti Family for their commitment to the city of Florence and to helping Florentine families in need&amp;rdquo; &lt;strong>declared Mayor Nardella. &lt;/strong>Thanks to the contribution of Menarini we have been able to renovate &lt;strong>40 apartments&lt;/strong> and we are counting on being able to continue this fruitful collaboration which benefits our entire community.&amp;rdquo; &amp;ldquo;As we have stated since the beginning of our &amp;nbsp;mandate &amp;ndash; explained the Mayor &amp;ndash; the housing policy is one of our priorities and we are working towards improving the actions taken to&amp;nbsp; deal with the housing crisis. We are working in a number of different ways: from public housing units, to social housing at a reduced rent rate, and second level accommodation. The target we have set ourselves is to create a system capable of responding to the different needs of citizens in difficulty.&amp;rdquo; &lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;ldquo;Once again we want to thank the Menarini Pharmaceutical Group and the Aleotti Family for their commitment to this project and for having invested, and continuing to invest, in the social sector&amp;rdquo; stated&amp;nbsp; the &lt;strong>Town Counsellor for Housing, Sara Funaro&lt;/strong>, &amp;ldquo;dedicating precious support to those families who need it most. Housing is a plight of our times and it is indeed one of the sectors in which we are deeply involved. As town counsel we are also seeking to guarantee social balance, not only in the public apartment buildings themselves but also during the assignment stage, through an attentive mediation between tenants and clear and effective condominium rules.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo;This is the fourth consecutive year that Menarini supports this solidarity project&amp;rdquo; declared &lt;strong>Lucia and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti &lt;/strong>&amp;ldquo;To date we have contributed towards changing the lives of forty&amp;nbsp; families and we couldn&amp;rsquo;t be prouder. We are filled with joy at the thought that this year, thanks to Menarini, many children can live and grow up in a safe and comfortable home. We hope that, for these children, this will be the first step towards a more serene future.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo;I would like to thank Menarini for this important contribution&amp;rdquo;, stated &lt;strong>the Chairman of Casa Spa, Talluri&lt;/strong>. &amp;rdquo;We are particularly proud that Casa Spa has been integrated into the system of relations established in the city of Florence.&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;table>&#xa;    &lt;tbody>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/1%20Assessore%20Comune%20Firenze%20Funaro%20Lucia%20Aleotti%20Sindaco%20Nardella%20consegnani%20una%20casa.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;Florence Town Counsellor Funaro, Lucia Aleotti, Mayor Nardella in one of the renovated apartments&quot; longdesc=&quot;Florence Town Counsellor Funaro, Lucia Aleotti, Mayor Nardella in one of the renovated apartments&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00001.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>Florence Town Counsellor Funaro, Lucia Aleotti, Mayor Nardella in one of the renovated apartments  &lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/Chiavi%20alloggiristrutturati%20da%20Menarini%20%20Firenze%20.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;Keys to the apartments in Florence renovated by Menarini&quot; longdesc=&quot;Keys to the apartments in Florence renovated by Menarini&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00002.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>Keys to the apartments in Florence renovated by Menarini&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/Lucia%20Aleotti%20sara%20Funaro%20Luca%20Talluri%20Alberto%20Giovanni%20Aleotti.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;Lucia Aleotti, Sara Funaro, Luca Talluri,Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&quot; longdesc=&quot;Lucia Aleotti, Sara Funaro, Luca Talluri,Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00003.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>Lucia Aleotti, Sara Funaro, Luca Talluri,Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/Sara%20funaro%20Sindaco%20Nardella%20Lucia%20Aleotti%20taglio%20del%20nastro%20alloggi%20popolari.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;Sara Funaro, Mayor of Florence Narddella, Lucia Aleotti at the ribbon - cutting at the public housing&quot; longdesc=&quot;Sara Funaro, Mayor of Florence Narddella, Lucia Aleotti at the ribbon - cutting at the public housing&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00004.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>Sara Funaro, Mayor of Florence Nardella, Lucia Aleotti at the ribbon - cutting at the public housing&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/Sindaco%20di%20firenze%20Dario%20Nardella%20Alberto%20Giovanni%20Aleotti%20.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&quot; longdesc=&quot;The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00005.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>The Mayor of Florence, Dario Nardella, and Alberto Giovanni Aleotti&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td style=&quot;width: 50%; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:dnnModal.show('/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/Sindaco%20Firenze%20Nardella%20Lucia%20Aleotti%20Presidente%20Menarini%20Sara%20Funaro%20Assessore%20Casa%20firenze%20Luca%20Talluri%20Casa%20Spa%20Alberto%20Giovanni%20aleotti%20Vice%20Presidente%20Menarini.jpg?popUp=true',false,720,1230,false)&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;The Mayor of Florence Nardella, Lucia Aleotti,Chairman of Menarini, Florence Town Counsellor for Housing Funaro, Luca Talluri Chairman Casa Spa&quot; longdesc=&quot;The Mayor of Florence Nardella, Lucia Aleotti,Chairman of Menarini, Florence Town Counsellor for Housing Funaro, Luca Talluri Chairman Casa Spa&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/consegna%20case/miniaturacasefirenze_00006.jpg&quot; />&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;p>&lt;em>The Mayor of Florence Nardella, Lucia Aleotti,Chairman of Menarini, Florence Town Counsellor for Housing Funaro, Luca Talluri Chairman Casa Spa&lt;/em>&lt;/p>&#xa;            &lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;    &lt;/tbody>&#xa;&lt;/table>"
